text:
You can’t do it easily, but via ::after hack you can do…
```a.lang_switcher_link{
    position:relative;
    text-indent: -999px;
}
a.lang_switcher_link:after {
    display: block;
    content: attr(data-language);
    text-indent: 0;
    position: absolute;
    top: 0;
    left: 0;
    padding: 0 10px;
}```
Note : you have to adjust style based on your need :wink:
